				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{CO}}_{2}=\left(\frac{\mathrm{GDP}}{\mathrm{Population}}\right)*\left(\frac{\mathrm{EC}}{\mathrm{GDP}}\right)*\left(\frac{\mathrm{FEC}}{\mathrm{EC}}\right)*(\frac{{\mathrm{CO}}_{2}}{\mathrm{FEC}})*(\mathrm{Population})$$\end{document}CO2=GDPPopulation∗ECGDP∗FECEC∗(CO2FEC)∗(Population)

